{"tid":1299160,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唔該大家咪撚再打飛機","createTime":"2019-07-09T03:58:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-09T05:01:39.000Z","uid":104500,"like":28,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"1489c6793294382a2052f7a24d936658069faf96","tid":1299160,"uid":104500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T03:58:51.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">五項訴求<br />\n一項都未達成</span></span><br />\n<br />\n而且法律就係得 <span style=\"color: red;\">撤回</span> 同 <span style=\"color: blue;\">押後</span><br />\n不論政府加上什麼花言巧語，但一日未正式宣佈撤回，一日都<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">只能視作押後</span><br />\n執著呢個字眼，唔係我地幼稚、唔係意氣用事，而係因為而家政府講嘅乜撚野「壽終正寢」、「暫緩」，都唔係議事規則入面所用嘅字眼！<br />\n<br />\n壽終正寢都還能借屍還魂，入土為安都還有頭七回魂，而且兄弟一個都未救到，惡法同暴動定義亦未被撤回<br />\n<br />\n借問聲大家係響度打乜撚野飛機？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔好同我袋住先！！！<br />\n唔好同我講我地贏左！！！<br />\n邊個再打飛機我就剪爛邊個條賓周！！！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ssFsrFr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FssFsrFr.jpg&h=cd51ad2b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a72c2afa9bd306e9e668824d326316e38d7e2e10","tid":1299160,"uid":104500,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T03:59:33.000Z","msg":"仲有個班分化撚，食你老母屎啦！<br />\n<br />\n叫得和理非就唔會同你衝，同佢地講和理非無用係想做乜鳩？叫佢地連街都唔好出唔好去遊行係咪？！支持唔係屌返黎架！<br />\n<br />\n亦唔准再屌勇武派！你有意見就去現場同佢地講！唔好成個睇完TVB就屌人嘅廢老一撚樣！！！<br />\n<br />\n兄弟爬山各有各做！唔好得個講字！！！！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6543b76325a1fa7c3e1a73fea3c54e34d7a358e5","tid":1299160,"uid":104500,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T04:01:19.000Z","msg":"麻煩各位響facebook見到有人話我地贏左，都佢地解釋返我地未贏呀！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19917ceef838221ba7d7ca426cf1c65f2876e48b","tid":1299160,"uid":104500,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T04:02:28.000Z","msg":"字眼好重要<br />\n五大訴求好重要<br />\n<br />\n政府而家明呃班外國人同真係以為贏左嘅傻仔呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec652aeb93517840faead381fa22d5675978532b","tid":1299160,"uid":104500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T04:04:19.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n收到班台灣fd恭喜我地香港勝利嘅msg真係心都寒撚埋"},{"pid":"19f07fed133c401ef6493eed3194ef66d2b4eb4e","tid":1299160,"uid":104500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T04:04:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />推呀"},{"pid":"d0a151588bf9fb3b317dcb3d5f1412d1215a6569","tid":1299160,"uid":236538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T04:04:38.000Z","msg":"不接受任何妥協<br />\n<br />\n集中立即實行雙真普選<br />\n<br />\n持久戰我們必敗<br />\n<br />\n刻不容緩！！！"},{"pid":"9f93cd298cf259825a56809049d2ba585e95ac28","tid":1299160,"uid":104500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T04:04:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00f1b9e30dba5b2e6dc3c23e7d039e8ebca56ebf","tid":1299160,"uid":104500,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d0a151588bf9fb3b317dcb3d5f1412d1215a6569","tid":1299160,"uid":236538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T04